primary

Class Initialization

  • java.lang.Object
    • primary.Initialization

  • public class Initialization
extends java.lang.Object
    Main class that holds major parameters, starts vital threads and initializes important objects. Contains the classes getWIFI that fetches the wifi parameters and startThreads that starts the display, odometer and sensors. Also contains initializeObjects that initializes the timer, the navigation and localization.
